                {
                    "id": "monotonic_increasing_depths",
                    "description": "Spot-checks the monotonic-increasing-with-depth invariant of the exponential grid (upstream `ExponentialGrid - Increasing Depth` test, roof_wall_road_snow_temperatures_test.jl:1016): z_node_1 < z_node_7 < z_node_15 and z_interface_1 < z_interface_8 < z_interface_16. Asserted via the spot values at three depths each — the full-column tests above already pin every layer, this test documents the monotonicity contract for downstream consumers.",
